2026-04-12 | Check Toeplitz Matrix

	Question
Return true if matrix is Toeplitz, else false.

	Approach
1.	Traverse matrix from (1,1) to (m-1,n-1)  
2.	For each cell:
		check mat[i][j] == mat[i-1][j-1]  
3.	If any mismatch → return false  
4.	If all match → return true  

	Time Complexity
	O(m × n)

	Space Complexity
	O(1)

	Solution

class Solution {
public:
    bool isToeplitz(vector<vector<int>>& mat) {

        int m = mat.size();
        int n = mat[0].size();

        for(int i = 1; i < m; i++){
            for(int j = 1; j < n; j++){
                if(mat[i][j] != mat[i-1][j-1])
                    return false;
            }
        }

        return true;
    }
};

	Key Insight
Every element must match its **top-left neighbor**.  
This ensures all diagonals have constant values → Toeplitz property satisfied.
